'''Cloudflare'''（Cloudflare, Inc.）是一家總部位於[[舊金山|舊金山]]的[[美國|美國]]跨國科技企業，以向客戶提供基於[[反向代理|反向代理]]的[[內容傳遞網路|內容傳遞網路]]（{{lang|en|Content Delivery Network, CDN}}）及[[域名系统|分佈式域名解析服務]]（{{lang|en|Distributed Domain Name Server}}）為主要業務。

== 歷史 ==

Cloudflare由三個曾為{{link-en|Project Honey Pot|Project Honey Pot}}工作的工程師Matthew Prince、Lee Holloway和Michelle Zatlyn於2009年創立，最終在<ref>{{cite web |language=en-us|url=https://www.cloudflare.com/our-story.html |title=Our story |author= |date= |work= |publisher=Cloudflare |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2015-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105170420/https://www.cloudflare.com/our-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en-us|url=http://www.projecthoneypot.org/cloudflare_beta.html |title=CloudFlare Beta |author= |date= |work= |publisher=Project Honey Pot |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204114508/http://www.projecthoneypot.org/Cloudflare_beta.html |archive-date=2017-12-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2010年9月舉行的[[TechCrunch_Disrupt|TechCrunch Disrupt]]大赛上首度公開出現。

2011年，駭客組織[[LulzSec|LulzSec]]使用Cloudflare的產品保护它的网站不被他人攻击，並在Twitter上赞扬此公司。Cloudflare因此於當年6月受到傳媒留意。<ref name="thewhir1">{{cite web |language=en-us|url=http://www.thewhir.com/web-hosting-news/cloudflare-gets-an-unusual-endorsement-from-hacker-group-lulzsec |title=CloudFlare Gets an Unusual Endorsement from Hacker Group LulzSec |first=Nicole |last=Henderson |date=2011-06-17 |work=Webhost Industry Review |publisher= |accessdate=2014-05-09 |archive-date=2017-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909050644/http://www.thewhir.com/web-hosting-news/Cloudflare-gets-an-unusual-endorsement-from-hacker-group-lulzsec |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="allthingsd1">{{cite web |language=en-us|url=http://allthingsd.com/20110610/web-security-start-up-cloudflare-gets-buzz-courtesy-of-lulzsec-hackers/ |title=Web Security Start-Up CloudFlare Gets Buzz, Courtesy of LulzSec Hackers |first=Arik |last=Hesseldahl |date=2011-06-10 |work=[[All_Things_Digital|All Things Digital]] |publisher= |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2011-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830110456/http://allthingsd.com/20110610/web-security-start-up-cloudflare-gets-buzz-courtesy-of-lulzsec-hackers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年7月，Cloudflare宣布來自{{tsl|en|New Enterprise Associates|恩颐投资|恩颐投资}}、{{tsl|en|Venrock|文洛克创投|文洛克创投}}及{{tsl|en|Pelion Venture Partners|珀利翁风投伙伴|珀利翁风投伙伴}}的新一輪[[風險投資|風險融資]]已經完成，金額為2000萬[[美元|美元]]。<ref>{{cite web |language=en-us|url=http://allthingsd.com/20110712/web-security-startup-cloudflare-lands-20-million-funding-round/ |title=Web Security Start-Up CloudFlare Lands $20 Million Funding Round |first=Arik |last=Hesseldahl |date=2011-07-12 |work= |publisher=AllThingsD |accessdate=2012-07-12 |archive-date=2012-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623222452/http://allthingsd.com/20110712/web-security-startup-cloudflare-lands-20-million-funding-round/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en-us|url= http://go.bloomberg.com/tech-deals/2012-12-18-why-a-fast-growing-startup-tries-to-keep-its-venture-funding-secret/ |title= Why a Fast-Growing Startup Tries to Keep Its Venture Funding Secret |last1= Milian |first1= Mark |last2=  |first2=  |date=2012-12-18|work= Tech Deals |publisher= [[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]] |accessdate=2013-01-01|archive-date= 2015-05-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150506073211/http://go.bloomberg.com/tech-deals/2012-12-18-why-a-fast-growing-startup-tries-to-keep-its-venture-funding-secret/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2012年6月，Cloudflare與數家虛擬主機提供者（包括 HostPapa）建立合作夥伴關係，以實作其Railgun技術。

2012 年 6 月，駭客組織{{tsl|en|UGNazi}} 利用[[Google|Google]]帳號驗證程序的缺陷入侵Cloudflare CEO {{lang|en|Matthew Prince}}的企業信箱，以此篡改著名社區網站[[4chan|4chan]]的Cloudflare帳號密碼並將它的DNS指向該組織的[[Twitter|Twitter]]主頁。<ref>{{cite web |language=en-us|url=http://www2.macleans.ca/2012/06/14/the-4chan-breach-how-hackers-got-a-password-through-voicemail/ |title=The 4chan breach: How hackers got a password through voicemail |first=Luke |last=Simcoe |date=2012-06-14 |work= |publisher=Maclean's |accessdate=2012-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130129222402/http://www2.macleans.ca/2012/06/14/the-4chan-breach-how-hackers-got-a-password-through-voicemail/ |archive-date=2013-01-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en-us|url= http://www.networkworld.com/community/blog/hacktivists-ugnazi-attack-4chan-cloudflare-and-wounded-warrior-project |title= Hacktivists UGNazi attack 4chan, CloudFlare and Wounded Warrior Project |author= Ms. Smith |date= 2012-06-03 |work= Privacy and Security Fanatic |publisher= NetworkWorld |accessdate= 2012-07-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131112193000/http://www.networkworld.com/community/blog/hacktivists-ugnazi-attack-4chan-Cloudflare-and-wounded-warrior-project |archive-date= 2013-11-12 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>

2012年12月，Cloudflare得到來自{{tsl|en|Union Square Ventures|合广投资|合广投资}}及其他現有投資方的C輪融資，其金額為5000萬[[美元|美元]]。<ref>{{cite web|language=en-us|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/12/17/cloudflare-reveals-50m-round-from-union-square-ventures/|title=CloudFlare Reveals $50M Round From Union Square Ventures|publisher=AOL|work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|accessdate=2015-01-05|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103041348/http://techcrunch.com/2013/12/17/cloudflare-reveals-50m-round-from-union-square-ventures/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

